WEBVTT

00:02.003 --> 00:03.959
[narrator] Previously on Lost:

00:04.046 --> 00:05.126
[wet thud]

00:06.883 --> 00:10.626
- You killed Naomi!
- She wants her people to come here.

00:10.720 --> 00:13.507
And trust me, when they do,
we had better be far away from here.

00:13.598 --> 00:16.055
If you want to live,
you need to come with me.

00:27.278 --> 00:29.018
- [Jack] Who are you?
- Daniel Faraday.

00:29.113 --> 00:30.523
I'm here to rescue you.

00:30.615 --> 00:33.778
[Naomi] This is the team? These are
the wrong people for this mission.

00:33.868 --> 00:36.701
None of them have field experience,
military training.

00:36.787 --> 00:39.779
You can't drop them in unprotected.
There's only so much I can do.

00:39.874 --> 00:42.490
Where's the chopper?
Where did it crash?

00:42.585 --> 00:46.203
What kind of pilot do you think I am?
I put her down safe and sound.

00:46.297 --> 00:48.879
- Get up. You're coming with us.
- We need to stay where we are

00:48.966 --> 00:51.708
- so they can find us.
- See, there's your problem.

00:51.802 --> 00:53.383
We don't want to be found.

00:53.471 --> 00:56.213
You want to know why we're here?
I'll tell you why.

00:56.307 --> 00:58.798
We're here for Benjamin Linus.

00:58.893 --> 01:01.054
Now where is he?

01:21.415 --> 01:24.407
[Jack] Did Ben mention knowing
anyone off the island?

01:24.502 --> 01:26.743
- You're sure of that?
- This is real simple.

01:26.837 --> 01:28.919
Do you know where he is, or don't you?

01:29.006 --> 01:31.998
- What do you want with him?
- I want to locate him.

01:32.093 --> 01:35.005
The people who hired me told me
his name's Benjamin Linus.

01:35.096 --> 01:37.553
They gave me this picture,
that's all he told me.

01:37.640 --> 01:40.256
They said find him.
And for what they're paying me,

01:40.351 --> 01:42.182
I don't need to know anything else.

01:43.062 --> 01:44.393
Do you?

01:46.023 --> 01:50.107
[Jack] You want Ben? OK,
he's with Locke and your friend...

01:50.194 --> 01:51.900
- [Miles] Charlotte.
- Charlotte.

01:51.988 --> 01:54.695
[Jack] Locke's got her too.
We know where he's heading.

01:54.782 --> 01:58.616
[Miles] Locke's the guy that killed
Naomi. Give me back my gun, Shephard.

01:58.703 --> 02:01.160
[Jack] You want your gun back,
I want answers.

02:01.247 --> 02:03.909
[Miles] You don't trust me,
I don't trust you.

02:04.000 --> 02:08.619
In fact, you're supposed to be dead.
Am I asking a billion questions? No.

02:08.713 --> 02:11.705
We both have the same problem,
this Locke guy.

02:11.799 --> 02:15.257
Even if Locke has your friend,
you can't waltz in there and grab her.

02:15.344 --> 02:17.801
- They're armed.
- How about that? So are we.

02:17.888 --> 02:20.721
- Why don't we move out...?
- You're not going anywhere.

02:20.808 --> 02:24.300
- Will that helicopter fly?
- It's what she does.

02:24.395 --> 02:27.387
- Then you can take me to your ship.
- Sayid, wait a second.

02:27.481 --> 02:30.689
We did call these people
to get us off this island, didn't we?

02:33.154 --> 02:34.940
Well?

02:35.031 --> 02:37.989
I burned a lot of fuel coming in.
I can't carry much weight.

02:38.075 --> 02:40.487
- I'll take three of you.
- In case you zoned out

02:40.578 --> 02:44.162
while tweezing your goatee, one
of these yahoos took Charlotte prisoner.

02:44.248 --> 02:46.330
I can bring her back safely.

02:50.421 --> 02:54.289
And if I do...
will you take me to the ship?

02:55.760 --> 02:57.000
Absolutely.

02:59.513 --> 03:01.720
You bring Charlotte back safe...

03:03.100 --> 03:05.386
...and I will take you off this island.

03:20.910 --> 03:23.401
[golf cart approaching]

03:27.875 --> 03:29.866
- Good morning.
- Good morning.

03:29.960 --> 03:33.452
It's a long walk to the next hole.
Do you need a ride?

03:33.547 --> 03:36.209
Thank you, but no.
My ball is right here.

03:36.300 --> 03:39.087
